Package: easynodecoind
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - daemon
 Easynodecoin is an experimental new digital currency that enables anonymous, instant
 payments to anyone, anywhere in the world. Easynodecoin uses peer-to-peer
 technology to operate with no central authority: managing transactions
 and issuing money are carried out collectively by the network. Easynodecoin Core
 is the name of the open source software which enables the use of this currency.
 .
 This package provides the daemon, easynodecoind, and the CLI tool
 easynodecoin-cli to interact with the daemon.

