Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - Qt GUI
 Easynodecoin is an experimental new digital currency that enables anonymous, instant
 payments to anyone, anywhere in the world. Easynodecoin uses peer-to-peer
 technology to operate with no central authority: managing transactions
 and issuing money are carried out collectively by the network. Easynodecoin Core
 is the name of the open source software which enables the use of this currency.
 .
 This package provides Easynodecoin-Qt, a GUI for Easynodecoin based on Qt.

Package: easynodecoin-tx
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer digital currency - standalone transaction tool
 Easynodecoin is an experimental new digital currency that enables anonymous, instant
 payments to anyone, anywhere in the world. Easynodecoin uses peer-to-peer
 technology to operate with no central authority: managing transactions
 and issuing money are carried out collectively by the network. Easynodecoin Core
 is the name of the open source software which enables the use of this currency.
 .
 This package provides easynodecoin-tx, a command-line transaction creation
 tool which can be used without a easynodecoin daemon.  Some means of
 exchanging minimal transaction data with peers is still required.
